    <h4>The Unsworth PPG latest newsletter</h4>

    <p>
      The Patient Participation Group (PPG) newsletter is produced as a special edition publication
      designed to highlight the important work and initiatives taking place both locally and nationally
      within healthcare. Its purpose is to keep our community informed, engaged, and confident in the
      developments shaping our services.
    </p>

    <p>
      We are committed to communicating in a way that is open, transparent, and easy to understand.
      Each edition aims to explain upcoming changes, share useful updates, and signpost practical
      sources of support that may benefit patients and their families.
    </p>

    <p>
      A new issue is released every three months, ensuring that information remains timely and relevant.
      If you would like to join our mailing list and receive future editions directly, please contact us at
      <a href="mailto:unsworthppg33@gmail.com">unsworthppg33@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>

